Title: Parasite
Plot: As the election and destruction of New York approach, Nathan meets up with Linderman. Hiro attempts to steal the sword heading him in a new path. Suresh and Sylar make progress with the list at great cost. D.L. begins to suspect problems at home. Isaac paints an even more terrible painting. A new hero, Candice Wilmer, appears.
GuestStars: Annie McKnight, Dutch Johnson, Martez Covington, Louis Iacoviello, David Barrera, Eugene Byrd, Ian Gomez, Malcolm McDowell
